txt.en: Naurúk can be found in the eastern stretch of the Beacon Hills.\n\nYou have encountered the keen-eyed Naurúk, and should defeat him.
You have defeated Naurúk before he could spot and send word of the Rohirrim host to the army of the Enemy.
A fell champion among the message-bearers in Far- Anórien sees all, hears all that goes by.

While exploring the Beacon Hills, you have encountered Naurúk in the eastern stretch of the Beacon Hills, keen of eyes and deadly of blade.\n\nDefeat Naurúk before he uses his fleet-footed message-bearers to share news of the Rohirrim host.
